name: Mangkok Ayam (Rooster Bowl)
description: The design is insipred by The Very Famous 'Mangkok Ayam' (Rooster Bowl). In Indonesia people who used to eat soup dishes such as meatballs, chicken noodles, porridge and others must be familiar with the 'Mangkok Ayam' illustration. In this design I want to spread one of the Indonesian Culture to the world with Modern representation of Mangkok Ayam using a geometric design style.
